<L>__{interior al ghazi's house same intercut with the haytham scene:}
<A>__{al ghazi sits on pillows on the living room with his wife and three daughters. a television is on, playing "man sayarbah al milioun" the arabic "who wants to be a millionaire." al ghazi's children are playing a game with peas, trying to guess which one of his hands al ghazi is hiding the pea. when a girl guesses correctly, he eats a pea. from outside, we hear the call to prayer. al ghazi and his family all move to prayer mats in his living room.}
